# Cloudflare Pages / Vercel SPA fallback + Legacy-Domain-Redirects.
# Per-route prerendered HTML (dist/<path>/index.html) is served verbatim if it exists.
# All other paths fall through to the SPA shell.
#
# Hardcut to BerufOS: 2026-05-25. Legacy domains (examfit.de, examfitwork.de,
# berufski.de) are 301-redirected to berufos.com on Cloudflare/Vercel.
# NOTE: Lovable hosting ignores _redirects — these activate only on the
# Vercel/Cloudflare migration (see docs/runbooks/vercel-migration.md).

# Legacy-Domain → BerufOS-Module
https://examfit.de/*       https://berufos.com/examfit/:splat       301!
https://www.examfit.de/*   https://berufos.com/examfit/:splat       301!
https://examfitwork.de/*   https://berufos.com/berufs-ki/:splat     301!
https://www.examfitwork.de/*  https://berufos.com/berufs-ki/:splat  301!
https://berufski.de/*      https://berufos.com/berufs-ki/:splat     301!
https://www.berufski.de/*  https://berufos.com/berufs-ki/:splat     301!

# Commerce-Naming-Migration: /bundle/* → /paket/* (on Cloudflare/Vercel,
# ignored on Lovable hosting — BundleToPaketRedirect handles it client-side).
/bundle/*    /paket/:splat    301
/bundle      /paket           301

/*    /index.html   200
